    {
      "id": "68",
      "name": "七聖召喚",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "プレイヤー紹介",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "協会認定プレイヤー。「八重堂」編集。最近は「七聖召喚」をテーマとする娯楽小説を考察するため、多大な労力をかけてカードゲームのルールを研究している！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "冒険挑戦",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "「黒の結界使い」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "ステージ紹介",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "冒険挑戦の物語の背景ですか、えっと…では、アビスの魔術師が儀式を行って、鳴神大社を呪おうとした…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ccbfad"
                      ],
                      "text": "【ヒント】同時に何種類もの「アビスの魔術師」と戦闘する時、「拡散」反応は予想外の効果を見せてくれることが…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "相手の編成",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3358,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/29/132746206/d0f899c3dfb0bbf999fd325030ed312d_2757190258950921280.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "アビスの魔術師・水",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3360,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/29/132746206/43d362bc5860c73bc0a10fc6e6f8f46d_2856463174289378482.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "アビスの魔術師・炎",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3359,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/29/132746206/26e0b8ef6539f2f8a1e3813a4ef93593_2333231882390309101.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "アビスの魔術師・氷",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "開放条件",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
